How to create the orbiter.jar file
==================================
In Eclipse : open "Jar export" tab, choose the packages to export and click export.

Files needed to run orbiter 
===========================
- jars/hme.jar
- jars/hme-host-sample.jar
- jars/simulator.jar
- jars/bananas.jar
- orbiter.jar

How to run with the simulator
=============================
java -cp jars/simulator.jar;orbiter.jar;jars/bananas.jar com.tivo.hme.sim.Simulator com.tivo.hme.orbiter.Orbiter

How to run stand-alone application
==================================
java -cp jars/hme.jar;jars/hme-host-sample.jar;jars/bananas.jar;orbiter.jar com.tivo.hme.host.sample.Main com.tivo.hme.orbiter.Orbiter

How to run stand-alone application on a specific port and interface
===================================================================
java -cp jars/hme.jar;jars/hme-host-sample.jar;jars/bananas.jar;orbiter.jar com.tivo.hme.host.sample.Main com.tivo.hme.orbiter.Orbiter --intf 10.0.0.89 --port 7288

